  "texts": [
    "Something that may be due to the programming simplicity of this game engine, which makes it suitable for multidisciplinary teams [38].",
    "If game engine usage is separated by the field of study of the first author, Unreal Engine has greater usage among history and archaeology specialists.",
    "Additionally, an analysis of the reconstruction characteristics revealed that Unreal Engine obtained a better score than Unity in both LoS (3.57 vs. 3.03) and LoD (3.88 vs. 3.02).",
    "These data coincided with the conclusions of other studies that underlined the hyper-realistic results of Unreal [16,20].In summary, conclusions regarding the design of 3DoF and 6DoF experiences will be obtained.",
